,"tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae694062df7d3688731ef296e7b653a78d0cc8a0","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06a47395ff1e19e09787a52282ecd0cbf00f138","tid":1047881,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=ff65d363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"48ccdee96fce307514d81812f45be36cb6b3a98b","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf8d2b9d2c81ad4b06fcde78528a19e46bc0ef8","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b4364f71016c14d1e8a9aab4ef0d3950f94759","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T19:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7544f9c5b9cadb9818c1c0ff3fabcee4182809f2","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ad84e0ebf9ff5b9c9e0bb4b3beb96d2bbcde67","tid":1047881,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"古代人們及醫學對於自慰多視為禁忌或邪惡︰西方古代視自慰為可怕的惡習，多做更會奪人性命，古代西醫有觀點指自慰是一種必須治療的病症，亦有醫生認為「最後會發瘋並且自殺」；中國古代就相傳「一滴精十滴血」，所以視為陋習，古代中醫亦有男性自慰有礙健康甚至導致性功能障礙的說法。現代大部份人對於自慰這一行為認為十分普通及正常的行為，亦沒有什麼不道德或不潔的想法，現代西方醫學亦認為自慰只要適可而止及著重衛生，對身體是無害。不過現在仍有不少思想保守、抱有原教旨主義的人，認為自慰是「傷身」、「不潔」、「不道德」及「邪惡」的一回事。"},{"pid":"e3f7b9194e9d5eda9338e10b66861fe12cd780ca","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafba8b8f39bef9625ec91ecc93b3ba73132ca3e","tid":1047881,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:51:13.000Z","msg":"咩年代"},{"pid":"810a48e2b36408fc27eb38d019b00d9fcb5acace","tid":1047881,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"九色鹿"},{"pid":"e1b6a6f2425d9d86fa00db33a505b4fa4a04fe41","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda8c962afb330367da8b75491b249ecd824be97","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1271c0a50bdaba5a0a3e35a021b4a1aec76eed","tid":1047881,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c1c3d24388d3c4565e7